CustomField.description: The names the organization trades under for commercial purposes. A 'trading style' or 'trading as a name' is a name a business chooses to use which is different from their registered company name. For example D&B is a trading style of Dun & Bradstreet Ltd. It is what the business chooses to call itself for marketing purposes.
